Package: cbuild
Title: Tools to Make Developing R Packages Interfacing with 'C' Easier
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Davis",
           family = "Vaughan",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "davis@rstudio.com")
Description: The goal of 'cbuild' is to provide two kinds of tools. The first
   set of tools allow for interactively compiling 'C' code in R. The second
   set of tools improve the workflow of an R package developer by automatically
   registering 'C' functions that should be exported to R.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
